1. First you have to rum: npm init
2. Import the enuke collection to the postman/thunderclient 
3. Then run index.js from the src directory


4. After this, hit the first api: 

localhost:3000/users
This will create a user in the database.


5. Then hit the next Api:

localhost:3000/users/me/avatar

Select the image you want to upload in the value field
This will upload the image for the authenticated user

6. API for logging the user in
localhost:3000/users/login

This will authenticate the user if the user gets logged out.

7. API for logging the user out
localhost:3000/users/logout
